### [AngstromAccumulatorReader](~/apps/ThetaSwap/thetaSwap-core-dev/.worktree/ranFromAngstrom/contracts/src/_adapters/LpRevenueAngstromOracleAdapter.sol)


We have a reader for [`globalGrowth`](https://app.angstrom.xyz/whitepaper-v1.pdf) denominated as $\mathcal{G}$ per block $b_i$:

$$
	\mathcal{G}_{b_i} =  \int_{b_0}^{b_i} g(b) db
$$

Where:

$$
	g(b) = \frac{S_b^{\star} - \sum_{j} \gamma_j(p_b^{\star})}{L_A (b)}
$$


